# Artisan Migration Rules (artisan-java only)

**SCOPE**: These rules apply ONLY to the artisan-java project. They do not affect other projects open in Cursor. If the request is not related to Artisan migration to Java, ignore these rules.

- **Source**: Python 3, PyQt5+, folder D:\project\artisantest-master (or workspace artisan-python equivalent)
- **Target stack**: Java 17, JavaFX 21, Chart-FX 11.2.7, AtlantaFX 2.0.1, jSerialComm 2.10.4
- **Architecture**: MVC (Model / View / Controller)
- **Naming**: Keep class names as in original (Python → Java)
- **Git**: One module = one branch; never move to the next module if the current one does not compile
- **Tests**: Write tests for every Model class
- **Comments**: English only
- **Style**: Google Java Style Guide
